text:
Value for money meal.  My Chicken Katsu Set is good.  Basically all can eat.  Where to get Full Spring Chicken for $10 in Singapore 🇸🇬 today.

Here you can get ½ Spring Chicken for $5. Full one for $10.

My apologies that I only decided to take a photo when I'm almost done with the meal.

I'm very glad to have had my meal here.
Ordered the Salmon Curry Rice and just wanted a little more rice, the store owner was so kind as to give me another spoon and when I asked how much? She just smiled and told me "it's okay"

This act of kindness really made my day, as it's not about the money but understanding that really goes a long way.

Thank you, I wish you business all the best!
One if the best most affordable japanese/ western food around Singapore! Highly recommend to come!!

This is probably the most affordable Japanese & western cuisine located in an industrial park.

Half spring chicken rice for $5. 哪里找！

😋😋😋😋😋😋😋😋

Price and portion ok. Just the chicken cutlet over-fried.
Salad is nice. Fries is hard. Chicken cutlet uses chicken breast, quite thick. Fish taste similar to ljs, but not crispy.
